In this page it is saying if FIPS enabled, on 3DES and TLS_RSA will be supported. Is this information up to date? 3DES is not allowed by Microsoft and FedRamp. TLS_ECDHA is providing forward secrecy, but it is not supported in FIPS mode if the statement is true.
